CLAUDE.md
.claude/

# Built language packs + localized scenarios are NOT committed. CI builds them in-run
# from the seedsigner-language-packs repo (checked out at a pinned ref) via its pinned
# GHCR toolchain image, and screens reads them from these gitignored dirs. Local dev:
# `scripts/ci/ci.sh build-fontpacks` (packs) + `scripts/ci/ci.sh gen-localized-scenarios`
# build them from a sibling ../seedsigner-language-packs checkout (override with
# $SS_LANGPACKS_REPO_DIR). Screens tests presentation, not the translation corpus, so
# nothing here needs to be tracked.
/lang-packs/
/tools/scenarios/localized/
# Throwaway scratch dir: dev screenshots, montages, zoom crops, fetched refs.
# (Was the untracked 'review/'; renamed to .tmp/ as a conventional scratch space.)
.tmp/
